direction: right

event: New message or scheduled follow-up
context: Context Builder\nOnly relevant tenant data
hermes: Hermes Agent Runtime
model: OpenAI model adapter
validate: Validate structured output
policy: Action Policy Engine

safe: Low-risk internal action\nTag, summarize, create task
review: Human approval\nReply, quotation, appointment
blocked: Block and log\nUnsupported or unsafe action

tools: Restricted Tool Gateway
audit: Audit log
outbox: Message outbox
crm: CRM modules
employee: Sales employee {
  shape: person
}

event -> context -> hermes -> model -> validate -> policy
policy -> safe: low risk
policy -> review: customer-facing or medium/high risk
policy -> blocked: forbidden
safe -> tools
review -> employee: request approval
employee -> review: approve, edit, or reject
review -> tools: approved
blocked -> audit
tools -> crm: controlled internal commands
tools -> outbox: approved outbound command
tools -> audit
